snippet.title: The Sims 3 Into the Future - Gameplay - Dystopian Future
snippet.description:
Will this be the Oasis Landing of your Sims future? Watch SimGuruBritney and SimGuruLauren's guided gameplay tour of a dystopian Oasis Landing. 

This expansion pack is now available. You can pick it up at your local retailer or on Origin: 
http://bit.ly/FutureSims3
